            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">No agency pitch. No optimization retainer.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Just an independent decision-grade assessment.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary inline-block">Request a diagnostic</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <a href="/blog" class="text-brand-blue font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to Blog</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
